{"tid":87164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【魂斷新娘潭】行山男疑影相跣腳 飛墮10米深崖底喪命","createTime":"2017-01-19T15:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T05:33:19.000Z","uid":28435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b352f9f3560d9f8bfd6ed0b5160536f73ad6fb6","tid":87164,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170119/large/1484820172_9750.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170119%2Flarge%2F1484820172_9750.jpg&h=e8ee083d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【20:23 更新】死者為退休教師<br />\n【19:35】傷者送院搶救不治<br />\n【18:55】警方懷疑傷者打算影相，取景期間跣腳墮下<br />\n【18:40】傷者由消防員救起，昏迷送院搶救<br />\n<br />\n56歲姓龍男子，今日到大埔新娘潭郊遊，至下午4時許，懷疑他於瀑布頂影相取景期間，不慎跣腳，飛墮10米深的崖底，頭部撼石重創，再反彈跌落水潭昏迷。有行山人士途經，發現龍的背囊於瀑布邊，未幾看見有人於水潭內載浮載沉，慌忙報案。救援人員接報到場，游繩落水潭救起龍，再由救護車送院搶救，惜終告不治。<br />\n<br />\n死者龍樹雲，人稱「龍Sir」，為退休教師，生前在一間教育出版社任職顧問，負責拍攝。龍Sir獨居於屯門，今早駕車前往上址獨自行山，順便拍攝，詎料失足墮崖慘死。"},{"pid":"57267eb44d65a98b8a078be81dd6f390fe35ebac","tid":87164,"uid":32322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:01:55.000Z","msg":"鬼新娘要新郎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fbb11057d66bc39d4f0a07ff9698760d7c36472","tid":87164,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0753545fa8a19770e2702e0d30c061c2363e4653","tid":87164,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:04:39.000Z","msg":"新娘潭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9226e5d42c42bf5b288f42d697deea056fd233","tid":87164,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:05:37.000Z","msg":"獨自行山點都危險啦"},{"pid":"0d851a0bd9a0109b02f24968f396f8aedec